Information.ShortDescription: Apart from Disneyland - it's the happiest place on earth!
Information.LongDescription: Exquisite. Urban. Chic. Enter a world like no other. A world unmatched in the Houston area. Cheval at Memorial has arrived as the newest, most grand apartment community Houston has ever seen. Our Mediterranean-style architecture features towering pillars and huge arches that will make you feel like youre on vacation every day of the year. You are surrounded by endless amenities and tantilizing features while conveniently located near I-10, the 610 Loop, the Galleria and Memorial Park. Cheval at Memorial didnt create the art of living well, we merely perfected it.
Information.DrivingDirections: From Downtown take I-10 West to the Washington exit. Make a right and follow to Old Katy Rd. (stay to the left). Were on your left.

Parking.Comment: Additional spaces may be available for an additional fee.

Pet.Comment: Family pets are welcome. Pet must be no larger than 35 pounds in weight and breed restrictions apply.

Information.ShortDescription: Washington DC apartments in Chinatown's Gallery Place!
Information.LongDescription: Avalon Gallery Place features studio, one, two, and three bedroom apartment homes just a block away from the Gallery Place/Chinatown Metro Station and the Verizon Center. Avalon Gallery Place apartments feature full size washers and dryers, kitchens with granite counters, gas stoves, and spacious closets. The Community includes a state of the art fitness center with Fitness On Demand, a rooftop terrace with views of DC's iconic landmarks, gas grills and free WiFi in the common areas.
